                                <p>卷軸</p>
                                <decoNote>
                                    The handscroll with narrow borders (小鑲手卷) features a protective and decorative backing (錦包首) crafted from yellowish beige 
                                    silk adorned with green and blue patterns. The title label is made of pale-brown Chinese paper. The 'Heaven' section (天) is 
                                    elegantly fashioned from pale-blue silk, exhibiting subtle signs of fading and staining. Vertical stripes (隔水) are composed 
                                    of white silk. The frontispiece (引首) is crafted from traditional Chinese paper in yellow, while the colophon section (拖尾) 
                                    is made from traditional Chinese white paper. The 'painted heart' (畫心) is crafted from yellow paper.
                                    小鑲手卷，錦包首為米黃色絲織物伴有藍色和綠色花紋，題簽為棕色紙本，八寶帶為棕色絲織物，別子已缺損。天為淺藍色有花紋絲織物，隔水為米白色有花紋絲織物，
                                    引首為黃色紙本，撞邊為黃色，拖尾為白色紙本。書法寫與黃色紙上。</decoNote>
